    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Alchemickal</strong></i> is a roguelite twin-stick shooter where frantic action collides with elemental mayhem. Step into the shoes of an everyday alchemist who’s in for <i>way</i> more than he signed up for.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Mix and Match</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107030/extras/ab524e12da02e629939ccfebd27780d8.poster.avif?t=1768509949\" width=780 height=434 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107030/extras/ab524e12da02e629939ccfebd27780d8.webm?t=1768509949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107030/extras/ab524e12da02e629939ccfebd27780d8.mp4?t=1768509949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your jury-rigged tech to imbue your weapons with <strong>chemickals</strong>, granting elemental properties to your attacks. Shock foes with chain lightning, melt them with acid, or coat them in flammable tar for a cascading explosion. Discover ancient recipes to unlock powerful new combinations!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Know Your Enemy</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107030/extras/56ce8b3bc15fd191f6fc1c3c624822f8.poster.avif?t=1768509949\" width=780 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107030/extras/56ce8b3bc15fd191f6fc1c3c624822f8.webm?t=1768509949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107030/extras/56ce8b3bc15fd191f6fc1c3c624822f8.mp4?t=1768509949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemies come with distinct quirks that shape every encounter: some bleed, others rust. Some can be tricked into attacking their own kin, others can have their powers sealed. Learn their tricks, exploit their weaknesses, and survive another floor.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Freedom of Expression</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107030/extras/4dbc0905a099d95b3786ba8f6649ee33.poster.avif?t=1768509949\" width=760 height=436 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107030/extras/4dbc0905a099d95b3786ba8f6649ee33.webm?t=1768509949\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3107030/extras/4dbc0905a099d95b3786ba8f6649ee33.mp4?t=1768509949\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every weapon has a unique upgrade tree, while an odd shop between worlds tempts you with bizarre buffs. Each run twists your arsenal into something new.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Gameplay Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced twin-stick combat that rewards quick thinking and improvisation.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A reactive alchemy system where elemental matchups and special recipes define your tactical options.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemies defined by both faction traits and elemental affinities for layered encounters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Permadeath: every run starts from the beginning.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Procedurally generated dungeons packed with hazards, ambushes, and other fun surprises.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An appealing shopkeeper.</p></li></ul>",
